---
title: Persian Freekeh Pilaf with Mango Halloumi and Balsamic Charred Peppers
description: We’ve packed extra flavour into this delicious dish by caramelising the halloumi in mango chutney. The sugar in the chutney loses its water content and starts to ‘brown’ which gives it a beautiful glossy texture and an amazing golden caramel flavour. We hope you enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/persian-freekeh-pilaf-wk43-60570818.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/persian-freekeh-pilaf-wk43-6c5e6cd8.pdf
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Middle Eastern
nutrition:
  calories: 677 kcal
  fat: 35 g
